 "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/318612351"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8I8sTAhaOcto5MEAMaCDMzMDc5MDU3II7dkOUFMA04wQJABXIJMzE4NjEyMzUxeACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "6_1678378059.3688247", "card_id": "Q_588464428", "card_label": {"type": "hot", "icon": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-266e83dbee46dce23b718e0531cb7d3a_1440w.png", "night_icon": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-c89199839c237b87e52f010bb5e7d773_1440w.png"}, "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 98}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "TVB 淘宝首播带货 2350 万，吸引超 485 万人观看，如何看待「港剧式直播」 掀起购物新热潮？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "3 月 7 日晚，TVB 淘宝直播间首次营业，吸引了超过 485 万人蹲守直播间，第一场带货 2350 万元。据了解，TVB 方面很看重和淘宝直播的合作，称其为「开创 TVB 电商直播的重大里程碑。」在高调官宣后，TVB 股价连日上涨，从 3.7 元涨至超过 11.5 元，增长近 3 倍，创下 TVB 历史最大涨幅。 TVB 入驻淘宝直播间引关注 「港剧式直播」能否掀起购物新热潮？"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pica.zhimg.com/80/v2-4bbb8478f0bbca63fcf0d005463b040f_720w.webp?source=1940ef5c"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "206 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/588464428"}}, "attached_info": "Cj8I8sTAhaOcto5MEAMaCDkzMDUxNDkzIM+0paAGMAI47gFABnIJNTg4NDY0NDI4eACqAQliaWxsYm9hcmTSAQA="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "7_1678378059.3695722", "card_id": "Q_588505752", "card_label": {"type": "hot", "icon": "https://pic2.zhimg.com/80/v2-266e83dbee46dce23b718e0531cb7d3a_1440w.png", "night_icon": "https://pic3.zhimg.com/80/v2-c89199839c237b87e52f010bb5e7d773_1440w.png"}, "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 95}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "尹锡悦将于 3 月 16 至 17 日访问日本，日韩互动升温，对东亚局势会有怎样影响？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": "据韩联社报道，韩国总统尹锡悦将于 3 月 16 日至 17 日访问日本。日前，韩国总统尹锡悦出席「三一独立运动 104 周年」纪念仪式时曾表示，希望韩日两国放弃历史恩怨，成为「拥有共同普世价值观的合作伙伴」。此后不久，尹锡悦政府公布日本二战时期强征劳工受害者赔偿问题的解决方案，韩方将设立公共赔偿基金，代替被告日企支付赔偿金和利息，由此引发韩国国内抗