的代言人，」贝弗利表示：「我喜欢莫兰特，他的前途一片光明，他在改变比赛。他为和他一样身材、运动能力以及背景的孩子打开了一扇门，所以他有这种责任，他需要做得更好。」 随后，贝弗利吐槽了莫兰特的父亲。「我成长过程中没有和父亲在一起，我看到莫兰特的爸爸每次都出现在场边，所以这种破事真不应该发生，他爸爸每天都在场边，他应该处理好这些事。」 此前，名记 Spears 建议灰熊签下安东尼。「把安东尼的更衣柜安排在莫兰特旁边，让他做莫兰特的导师。」安东尼职业生涯早期也被一些恶劣事件困扰，但他后来专注于篮球生涯，成为超级球星。Spears 认为莫兰特能从这段经历中受益。名记：莫兰特可能禁赛 50 场！贝弗利吐槽莫父 灰熊该签甜瓜当导师？"}, "image_area": {"url": "https://picx.zhimg.com/80/v2-14ab342f106025af4d7c94158f0c8d29_720w.webp?source=1940ef5c"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "39 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/588238367"}}, "attached_info": "Cj4I8sTAhaOcto5MEAMaCDkzMDAxNDQ5IOHRn6AGMAA4FEAdcgk1ODgyMzgzNjd4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA=="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "30_1678378059.386519", "card_id": "Q_584348375", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 48}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "经济学常识普及为什么这么难？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": ""}, "metrics_area": {"text": "39 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/584348375"}}, "attached_info": "Cj4I8sTAhaOcto5MEAMaCDkyMTM2OTcwIJn8tZ8GMAA4d0Aecgk1ODQzNDgzNzV4AKoBCWJpbGxib2FyZNIBAA=="}, {"type": "hot_list_feed", "style_type": "1", "id": "31_1678378059.3869572", "card_id": "Q_588456341", "feed_specific": {"answer_count": 19}, "target": {"title_area": {"text": "22-23 赛季 NBA 快船 108:100 猛龙，小卡 24+12，如何评价这场比赛？"}, "excerpt_area": {"text": ""}, "image_area": {"url": "https://pic4.zhimg.com/50/v2-0a70822054fab0a85113af42ef1e9ae7_b.jpg"}, "metrics_area": {"text": "39 万热度", "font_color": "", "background": "", "weight": ""}, "label_area": {"type": "trend", "trend": 0, "night_color": "#B7302D", "normal_color": "#F1403C"}, "link": {"url": "https://www.zhihu.com/question/588456341"}}, "attached_i